('sC4ZLZ8x', 'Russian', '{COMMENT}'),
('SCaWkKF1', 'Russian', 'Here is what we''ve promised, {GOLD_REWARD}{GOLD_ICON} denars. I hope this makes it worth the blood spilled.'),
