('scQJw4Hg', 'Russian', 'Да, мой муж?'),
('SCsFatSc', 'Russian', 'SteppeHair Описание'),
('ScSV97Dm', 'Russian', 'We are preparing for an attack but we need some time to gather our men. Meet me here in {SETTLEMENT_NAME} after 3 days and we''ll strike them together.'),
